scripts.dev: VITE_COMMIT_SHA="$(git rev-parse --short HEAD 2>/dev/null || echo 'dev')" VITE_COMMIT_SUBJECT="$(git log -1 --pretty=format:%s 2>/dev/null || echo '')" VITE_COMMIT_BODY="$(git log -1 --pretty=format:%b 2>/dev/null | tr '\n' ' ' || echo '')" vite
scripts.build: VITE_COMMIT_SHA="$(git rev-parse --short HEAD 2>/dev/null || echo 'dev')" VITE_COMMIT_SUBJECT="$(git log -1 --pretty=format:%s 2>/dev/null || echo '')" VITE_COMMIT_BODY="$(git log -1 --pretty=format:%b 2>/dev/null | tr '\n' ' ' || echo '')" vite build
